(17, 155, 'Support Us ', 'support-us', '<p>Join us in creating an inclusive artistic space where creativity thrives and cultural heritage is celebrated. Here\'s how you can help:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Volunteer:</strong></span> Share your time and expertise to assist with events and workshops.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Donate:</strong></span> Support our art education programs and emerging artists with a generous contribution.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Sponsorship:</strong></span> Collaborate with us to showcase your brand and support our mission.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Spread the Word:</strong></span> Share our website and events with your network.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Attend:</strong> Join us at our art events, workshops, and exhibitions.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>For more information, contact Aleme Tadesse at catch<a href=\"mailto:aleme@beteseb.org\" target=\"_new\">aleme@gmail.com </a>or call +1 (202) 45-3117.</p>\r\n<p>Together, let\'s empower young people, foster creativity, and embrace our cultural heritage through the arts.<br /><br />++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++</p>\r\n<div class=\"flex-1 overflow-hidden\">\r\n<div class=\"react-scroll-to-bottom--css-uzxis-79elbk h-full dark:bg-gray-800\">\r\n<div class=\"react-scroll-to-bottom--css-uzxis-1n7m0yu\">\r\n<div class=\"flex flex-col text-sm dark:bg-gray-800\">\r\n<div class=\"group w-full text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 border-b border-black/10 dark:border-gray-900/50 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-[#444654]\">\r\n<div class=\"flex p-4 gap-4 text-base md:gap-6 md:max-w-2xl lg:max-w-[38rem] xl:max-w-3xl md:py-6 lg:px-0 m-auto\">\r\n<div class=\"relative flex w-[calc(100%-50px)] flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3 lg:w-[calc(100%-115px)]\">\r\n<div class=\"flex flex-grow flex-col gap-3\">\r\n<div class=\"min-h-[20px] flex flex-col items-start gap-4 whitespace-pre-wrap break-words\">\r\n<div class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert light\">\r\n<h5><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><strong>Urgent Space Needed for Weekly Painting Sessions - Beteseb African Heritage Art Center</strong></span></h5>\r\n<p>Attention Community Members,</p>\r\n<p>Beteseb African Heritage Art Center, a startup non-profit organization dedicated to fostering art, cultural heritage, and community engagement, is in urgent need of a space to host our weekly painting sessions for kids and adults.</p>\r\n<p>With nine years of experience organizing painting events, we have witnessed the transformative power of art. These sessions provide a nurturing environment for artistic expression and personal growth.</p>\r\n<p>We are reaching out to our community for immediate assistance in finding a suitable venue for our painting sessions. The space is urgently needed to accommodate our upcoming sessions. We are looking for a location that offers:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Sufficient room for group gatherings</li>\r\n<li>Art-friendly environment with natural light and good ventilation</li>\r\n<li>Accessibility by public transportation and parking facilities</li>\r\n<li>Basic amenities such as tables, chairs, and restrooms</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>By providing a space, you would greatly contribute to the growth of our startup non-profit and support the arts within our community. We are more than willing to acknowledge your generous support through our marketing efforts and social media channels.</p>\r\n<p>If you have any available spaces or suggestions, we kindly request you to reach out to us at <a href=\"mailto:catchaleme@gmail.com\">catchaleme@gmail.com</a>. Your prompt assistance in this matter would be highly appreciated.</p>\r\n<p>Thank you for your support in helping us create an inclusive and vibrant artistic space for our community.</p>\r\n<p>Warm regards,</p>\r\n<p> Beteseb African Heritage Art Center (Startup Non-Profit)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>.</p>', '', 1, 2, '2023-04-04 03:55:31', 918, '', '2023-06-13 02:39:52', 918, NULL, NULL, '2023-04-04 03:55:31', NULL, '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":\"\",\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":\"\",\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":\"\",\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 9, 0, '', '', 1, 325, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\"}', 0, '*', ''),
(18, 156, 'Painting as a family ', 'painting-as-a-family', '<p>Nothing brings a family closer than engaging in a fun and creative activity together. At Beteseb African Heritage Art Center, we believe that painting as a family is not only an enjoyable experience but also a way to create lasting memories.</p>\r\n', '\r\n<p><br />In one of our recent painting sessions, we had the privilege of witnessing a beautiful family moment that exemplified the power of art to unite generations.</p>\r\n<p> Picture this: Grand Ma, her son, and granddaughter, all gathered around a canvas, paintbrushes in hand, and hearts filled with excitement. It was a sight to behold at Beteseb African Heritage Art Center, where families come together to explore their artistic talents and bond over the joy of painting.</p>\r\n<p>The atmosphere was buzzing with laughter, chatter, and creative energy as each family member expressed themselves through vibrant strokes of paint. The intergenerational exchange of ideas and techniques made the experience even more enriching. From sharing stories and memories to offering guidance and support, painting as a family became a whole new experience that transcended age barriers.</p>\r\n<p> </p>', 1, 9, '2023-06-13 02:54:38', 918, '', '2023-06-17 03:34:25', 918, NULL, NULL, '2023-06-13 02:54:38', NULL, '{\"image_intro\":\"images\\/banners\\/5b349863-689e-4c06-adae-bc53d8981552.jpg#joomlaImage:\\/\\/local-images\\/banners\\/5b349863-689e-4c06-adae-bc53d8981552.jpg?width=1024&height=768\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":\"\",\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":\"\",\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":\"\",\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 5, 0, '', '', 1, 55, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\"}', 0, '*', '');
