(83, 'com_content.article.17', '', '2023-06-07 02:46:32', 918, 3577, '3ed736df038b97f187a53b259b5efe9f8782ad5d', '{\"id\":\"17\",\"asset_id\":155,\"title\":\"Support Us \",\"alias\":\"support-us\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Join us in our mission to create an inclusive and vibrant artistic space where creativity thrives, cultural heritage is celebrated, and young people connect with their roots while embracing their American identity. Here\'s how you can support us:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ol>\\r\\n<li>\\r\\n<p>Volunteer: Share your time and expertise by volunteering with us. Help us organize events, assist with workshops, or contribute your skills in areas such as marketing, administration, or fundraising.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>\\r\\n<p>Donate: Your generous donations allow us to continue providing art education programs, organizing community events, and supporting emerging artists. Every contribution, no matter the size, makes a difference.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>\\r\\n<p>Sponsorship: Partner with us as a sponsor to support our initiatives and gain exposure for your brand. Collaborate with us on events, exhibitions, or workshops to showcase your commitment to the arts and community engagement.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>\\r\\n<p>Spread the Word: Help us expand our reach by spreading the word about Bet\'eseb Nonprofit Art Center. Share our website, social media posts, and events with your friends, family, and colleagues who may be interested in our mission.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>\\r\\n<p>Attend Our Events: Participate in our art events, workshops, and exhibitions. Your presence not only supports our organization but also provides inspiration and encouragement to the artists and participants involved.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>\\r\\n<p>Collaborations: If you represent an organization or business aligned with our mission, we welcome collaborative opportunities to create mutually beneficial projects that promote art, culture, and community engagement.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\\r\\n<p>By supporting Bet\'eseb Nonprofit Art Center, you help us empower young people to express their creativity, explore their heritage, and develop a sense of belonging. Together, we can make a lasting impact through the arts.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":2,\"created\":\"2023-04-04 03:55:31\",\"created_by\":\"918\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2023-06-07 02:46:32\",\"modified_by\":918,\"checked_out\":918,\"checked_out_time\":\"2023-06-07 02:40:44\",\"publish_up\":\"2023-04-04 03:55:31\",\"publish_down\":null,\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":