(120, 'com_content.article.8', '', '2023-06-17 03:06:45', 918, 3305, 'f6d5ca88deadd6eb2dbe2acf6954fdfbe73f02e6', '{\"id\":\"8\",\"asset_id\":130,\"title\":\"Home \",\"alias\":\"home\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Welcome to Beteseb African Heritage Art Center!<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>As a non-profit organization, our mission is to celebrate and promote African heritage through the power of art. For nine years, Beteseb has been a thriving hub of artistic activity, working with various organizations and businesses to create meaningful experiences.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>We believe in investing in the creative potential of young people and aim to expand our repertoire to encompass other art forms, such as sculpture, photography, dance, and music. At Beteseb, we provide a vibrant space where art enthusiasts, artists, and the community come together to engage, learn, and be inspired.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Throughout our journey, we have had the privilege of partnering with a wide range of organizations that share our vision. We have collaborated with esteemed institutions, community organizations, and businesses to create impactful art initiatives. To see a list of our past partners, please click here.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Join us at Beteseb African Heritage Art Center as we continue to work with organizations and businesses to promote African heritage and create unforgettable artistic encounters.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Thank you for visiting Beteseb, and we look forward to embarking on this artistic journey with you.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The Beteseb Team<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":2,\"created\":\"2023-04-04 02:21:41\",\"created_by\":\"918\",\"created_by_alias\":\"Joomla\",\"modified\":\"2023-06-17 03:06:45\",\"modified_by\":918,\"checked_out\":918,\"checked_out_time\":\"2023-06-17 03:05:44\",\"publish_up\":\"2023-04-04 02:21:41\",\"publish_down\":null,\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/headers\\\\\\/Article%20Home%20Image.jpg#joomlaImage:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/local-images\\\\\\/headers\\\\\\/Arti