(121, 'com_content.article.8', '', '2023-06-17 03:15:58', 918, 3660, '413a58995115d5cdf82c7da3051f04ad8f4aa7ce', '{\"id\":\"8\",\"asset_id\":130,\"title\":\"Home \",\"alias\":\"home\",\"introtext\":\"<p>For the past nine years, Beteseb African Heritage Art Center has been an artistic oasis, a bustling hub of creativity and inspiration. Our vibrant space has been alive with the energy of countless individuals, organizations, and businesses coming together to celebrate the power of art. And now, we are thrilled to share our exciting news with you: Beteseb has officially transitioned into a non-profit organization!<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>This new chapter in our journey opens up a world of possibilities. As a non-profit, we have the freedom to expand our reach, deepen our impact, and continue our mission of celebrating and promoting African heritage through the captivating medium of art.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>At Beteseb, we are strong believers in the transformative potential of the arts, especially for the younger generation. We envision a future where the creative spark within every young person is nurtured and ignited. That\'s why we are dedicated to expanding our repertoire beyond painting to include other art forms such as sculpture, photography, dance, and music. Our goal is to provide a dynamic and inclusive space where art enthusiasts, artists, and the community can come together to engage, learn, and be inspired.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>We invite you to join us at Beteseb African Heritage Art Center as we embark on this thrilling artistic journey. Together, we will continue to work with organizations and businesses to promote African heritage, create unforgettable artistic encounters, and make a positive difference in our community.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Thank you for visiting Beteseb, and get ready to be swept away by the magic of art!<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The Beteseb Team<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":2,\"created\":\"2023-04-04 02:21:41\",\"created_by\":\"918\",\"created_by_alia