\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":13,\"ordering\":0,\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":1,\"hits\":539,\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"1\",\"language\":\"*\",\"note\":\"\"}', 0),
(122, 'com_content.article.8', '', '2023-06-17 03:21:34', 918, 16354, '6f1ffc585360a7e66397df69fe400a752d11d4c7', '{\"id\":\"8\",\"asset_id\":130,\"title\":\"Home \",\"alias\":\"home\",\"introtext\":\"<div class=\\\"flex-1 overflow-hidden\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"react-scroll-to-bottom--css-jukgg-79elbk h-full dark:bg-gray-800\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"react-scroll-to-bottom--css-jukgg-1n7m0yu\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"flex flex-col text-sm dark:bg-gray-800\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"group w-full text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 border-b border-black\\/10 dark:border-gray-900\\/50 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-[#444654]\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"flex p-4 gap-4 text-base md:gap-6 md:max-w-2xl lg:max-w-[38rem] xl:max-w-3xl md:py-6 lg:px-0 m-auto\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"relative flex w-[calc(100%-50px)] flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3 lg:w-[calc(100%-115px)]\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"flex flex-grow flex-col gap-3\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"min-h-[20px] flex flex-col items-start gap-4 whitespace-pre-wrap break-words\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert light\\\">\\r\\n<p>For the past nine years, Beteseb African Heritage Art Center has been an artistic oasis, redefining entertainment and pastimes for young people and art enthusiasts alike. Our vibrant space has been alive with the energy of countless individuals, organizations, and businesses coming together to celebrate the power of art. And now, we are thrilled to share our exciting news with you: Beteseb has officially transitioned into a non-profit organization!<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>This new chapter in our journey opens up a world of possibilities. As a non-profit, we have the freedom to expand our reach, deepen our impact, and continue our mission of celebrating and promoting African heritage through the captivating medium of art.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>At Beteseb, we are strong believers in the transformative potential of the arts, especially for the younger generation. We are dedicated to redefining entertainment and pastimes for young people, providing them with a vibrant space where they can engage, learn, and be inspired. From our painting events to workshops and performances, we offer a diverse range of experiences that capture their imagination and ignite their creative spirit.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>We envision a future where young people embrace the arts as a source of joy, self-expression, and cultural exploration. That\'s why we are committed to expanding our repertoire beyond painting to include other art forms such as sculpture, photography, dance, and music. Our goal is to create a dynamic and inclusive environment where young artists can thrive and where the community can come together to appreciate and celebrate African heritage.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>We invite you to join us at Beteseb African Heritage Art Center as we embark on this thrilling artistic journey. Together, we will continue to redefine entertainment and pastimes for young people, promote African heritage, create unforgettable artistic encounters, and make a positive difference in our community.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Thank you for visiting Beteseb, and get ready to be swept away by the magic of art!<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The Beteseb Team<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"flex justify-between lg:block\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"text-gray-400 flex self-end lg:self-center justify-center mt-2 gap-2 md:gap-3 lg:gap-1 lg:absolute lg:top-0 lg:translate-x-full lg:right-0 lg:mt-0 lg:pl-2 visible\\\"><button class=\\\"flex ml-auto gap-2 rounded-md p-1 hover:bg-gray-100 hover:text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 dark:hover:text-gray-200 disabled:dark:hover:text-gray-400\\\"><\\/button>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"flex gap-1\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"group w-full text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 border-b border-black\\/10 dark:border-gray-900\\/50 dark:bg-gray-800\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"flex p-4 gap-4 text-base md:ga